  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "How did Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "斯特林太太"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Stirling get her bag back?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是怎样拿回提包的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "安·"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Ann Stirling did not think of the risk she was taking when she ran through a forest after two men.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "斯特林太太追着两个男人跑进森林时，根本没想到自己所冒的风险。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "They had rushed up to her while she was having a picnic at the edge of a forest with her children.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "当时她正和孩子们在森林边缘野餐，那两个人突然冲到她面前。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "斯特林"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Stirling got so angry that she ran after them.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "太太气愤极了，便追了上去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "She was soon out of breath, but she continued to run.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她很快就上气不接下气，但仍继续追赶。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "When she caught up with them, she saw that they had sat down and were going through the contents of the bag, so she ran straight at them.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "追上他们时，她看到两人已经坐下，正在翻看包里的东西，于是径直朝他们冲过去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "The men got such a fright that they dropped the bag and ran away.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那两个人吓得扔下提包逃走了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "The strap needs mending, said Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“包带需要修一修，”斯特林太太"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Stirling later, but they did not steal anything.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "后来又说，“不过他们什么也没偷走。”"
      }
    }
  ],
